data.description:
*SELLER IS OFFERING $10,000 IN CONCESSIONS FOR RATE BUY DOWN* Great home nestled in the picturesque community of Joshua, this 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom home offers a perfect blend of modern comfort and country living charm. Features include Spacious and open living areas that provide an ideal space for entertaining or family gatherings.
A well-equipped kitchen with tons of cabinets, pot filler by range oven, and an ample amount of counter space. A generous 1.7 acre lot with plenty of room for outdoor activities, gardening and large covered patio. Do not miss the opportunity to make this charming house your forever home!
